    {
      "id": "node-m3-model",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# MiniMax M3\n\nOpen-weights frontier model (Jun 2026)\n1M context · multimodal · computer use\n\n59% SWE-Bench Pro\n70.06% OSWorld-Verified\n83.5 BrowseComp",
      "x": -1500,
      "y": -1300,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-msa",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# MSA Sparse Attention\n\nKV-block selection\n1/20 per-token compute at 1M\n9.7× prefill · 15.6× decode\nKV-outer-gather-Q",
      "x": -1000,
      "y": -1300,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-1m",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# 1M Context\n\nWhole-vault as working memory\nWhole-codebase in one thread\nCompaction at 50K intervals\n\nLost-in-middle still applies",
      "x": -500,
      "y": -1300,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-multimodal",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Native Multimodality\n\nText + image + video input\nNo OCR / Whisper pipeline\nScreenshot-as-input\nLoom-as-input",
      "x": 0,
      "y": -1300,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-cu",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Computer Use\n\n70.06% OSWorld-Verified\nScreenshot → action → screenshot\na11y tree + Set-of-Marks\nNative vision = no separate pipeline",
      "x": 500,
      "y": -1300,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-soul",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# SOUL V2 (Operator Contract)\n\nEA mode · direct, no fluff\nReconfirm before irreversible\nQuote what you read\n\nHard constraints:\n• no deploys without approval\n• no push to non-vault\n• no destructive ops without go",
      "x": -1500,
      "y": -500,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-vellum",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Vellum Architecture\n\nCHIEF templates (pattern/idea/question)\n + Vellum structural layer\n\nVault = primary memory\nContext-budget allocator\nNo chunking by default",
      "x": -950,
      "y": -500,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-workflow",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Mavis EA Workflow\n\nCapture over polish\nLink on reference, processing, review\nSpec-audit before execution\nReport gaps, wait for \"go\"",
      "x": -450,
      "y": -500,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-curator",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# long-context-curator\n\nMCP #3 — packs context for M3\nanchor-ends strategy\nmarginal-value scoring\nCompaction at 50K intervals",
      "x": 50,
      "y": -500,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-self-card",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# self-model-card\n\nMCP #5 — agent introspection\nWhat tools · what memory · what state\n\nself.can_i() = pre-flight check\nEnforces SOUL V2 at runtime",
      "x": 550,
      "y": -500,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-vault-brain",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# vault-brain\n\nMCP #1 — semantic vault search\nHybrid: embeddings + wikilink graph\nToken-budget controlled\nWhole-vault in-context mode",
      "x": -1500,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-vision-anchor",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# macos-vision-anchor\n\nMCP #2 — persistent visual state\nCross-session anchors\na11y tree + Set-of-Marks\nvision_anchor.diff() for change tracking",
      "x": -950,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-healer",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# tool-self-healer\n\nMCP #4 — production reliability\nClassify error → apply recovery\nCache successful patterns\n<1ms on repeat, $0 LLM cost",
      "x": -400,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-cu-mcp",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# cu (Computer Use) MCP\n\nGeneric tier-3 execution\nscreenshot · click · type\nCurrently stateless\nmacos-vision-anchor adds memory",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-generic-mcp",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Generic MCP stack\n\nfilesystem · git · fetch · shell\nplaywright · obsidian · supabase\nkanban · matrix · playwright\n\nTier 1+2 of execution",
      "x": 650,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-macos",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# macOS APIs\n\nAXUIElement (a11y tree)\nCGEvent (input)\nQuartz Display (capture)\nAppKit / Cocoa\n\nTouchID / sudo = real gates",
      "x": -1500,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-obsidian",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Obsidian Vault\n\nThis vault (MiniMax-Agent/)\n00 Inbox → 01 Daily → 02 Notes\n03 Projects → 04 Resources → 99 _system\n\nFTS5 search · wikilinks · graph view\n~2-5K notes, 1-2M tokens",
      "x": -950,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-network",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Network APIs\n\nCalendar · Gmail · Drive\nSheets · Notion · Slack\nOpenAI-compat endpoints\nSupabase · HuggingFace · MiniMax API",
      "x": -450,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-apps",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# GUI Apps (Tier 3 territory)\n\nAnything with no API:\nLegacy enterprise software\nGovernment portals\nNiche SaaS · local desktop tools\n\nDriven via cu + macos-vision-anchor",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-filesystem",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Local Filesystem\n\nThe vault repo (git)\nLocal scripts + binaries\n\nTrash, not rm (recoverable)\nGit commits pre-Phase, push on GO",
      "x": 550,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "node-m3-flow",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Data flows ↑↓\n1. Prompt → M3 (1M context + multimodal)\n2. M3 → Intelligence: tool calls + reasoning\n3. Intelligence → Execution: invoke MCP\n4. Execution → Host OS: API call / GUI action\n5. Host OS → Execution: state / response\n6. Execution → Intelligence: result + state\n7. Intelligence → M3: next prompt\n\nLoop time: 200ms (API) to 5s (visual)",
      "x": -1500,
      "y": -1500,
      "width": 3000,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    }
  ],
